---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy · Stillpoint" description="How Stillpoint handles your data — briefly, plainly, and with respect." path="/privacy">
  <Nav />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 prose-like">
    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl text-purple-900">Privacy</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-purple-900/70 leading-relaxed">
      We collect the smallest amount of information possible. If you join the waitlist we store your email address in a
      Supabase database on our infrastructure, and send you a confirmation via Resend. We do not share your email
      with third parties. We do not run ads. We do not track you.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-purple-900/70 leading-relaxed">
      When the app ships, practice history stays on your device. Anonymous crash reports may be used to fix bugs and
      are never tied to your identity. You can request deletion of your waitlist record by replying to any email we send you.
    </p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
